cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.DB, cs.CL, cs.PL 

Reasoning: 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the development of intelligent systems based on Logic Programming technology for solving computational problems. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is also a likely category as the paper focuses on the design of an expressive logic suitable for declarative knowledge representation. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is another possible category as the paper discusses the integration of aggregates into ID-logic, which is used for declarative knowledge representation and solving computational problems. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a possible category as the paper discusses the development of abductive solvers for a language used for knowledge representation. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the development of a solver for a logic programming language.
